   </svg>
  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h3>
<p>Reason codes are configured for agents to select a reason while going not ready and/or logging out.&nbsp;</p>
<p>To add a reason, go to the <strong>Reason Codes&nbsp;</strong>list and create a new reason using the following table:</p>
<div class="theme-table" style="--width: 1800px;">
 <table-expand>
  <scroll-shadow>
   <table-sort>
    <div data-component="table" data-align="unset" data-number-column="false">
