  </copy-clipboard>
 </i18n-message></h3>
<p>A default Wrap-up form is available on the <strong>Forms&nbsp;</strong>page. &nbsp;</p>
<p>Go to the form, <strong>WrapUp </strong>and select edit action against the form to add wrap-up categories and reasons as per your business needs.&nbsp;</p>
